            . I live in Fleet-street; I am a tallow chandler</p>
               <p>Q. Are you a customer of Mr. Hill and Parkinson. - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. What is the prisoner. - A. He was my <rs id="t18070916-135-deflabel723" type="occupation">porter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070916-135-defend1136 t18070916-135-deflabel723"></join>; he left me in April. I never sent him for these candles, nor did I ever see him.</p>
